              ZURK IX: "The Rendezvous"                                         In the climactic conclusion of the Zurk saga, the adventurer finds himself      in an incredible and large world where he must battle his way through a vast    assortment of monsters and puzzles and dungeons.                                END                                                                             In the finale he finally realizes he is in a huge spacecraft, and ultimately    finds his way to its helm.                                                      END                                                                             Therein he meets an incredible alien being who calls herself a "Starchild",     and has welcomed him to what is like a sandbox to her. Even as she teleports    him back to his own world, he feels that this is indeed the one he's seen       END                                                                             in his other quests, and resolves to one day meet her in fully human form,      hoping all his questions will be answered.                                      FINISH                                                                          